   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Product Description Generator\\n\",\"**NLP Project 56 of 100** — Generate e-commerce product descriptions from metadata using templates and LLMs.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Use structured metadata to generate natural text.\\n\",\"2. Compare template-based vs LLM-generated descriptions.\\n\",\"3. Evaluate quality of generated marketing copy.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, requests, json\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nSEED = 42; rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"products = [\\n    {'name':'Wireless Earbuds Pro','category':'Electronics','price':79.99,'features':['Active noise cancellation','30hr battery','Water resistant IPX5']},\\n    {'name':'Organic Cotton T-Shirt','category':'Clothing','price':29.99,'features':['100% organic cotton','Fair trade certified','Available in 8 colors']},\\n    {'name':'Smart Fitness Tracker','category':'Electronics','price':49.99,'features':['Heart rate monitor','Sleep tracking','7-day battery life']},\\n    {'name':'Premium Coffee Beans','category':'Food','price':18.99,'features':['Single origin Ethiopian','Medium roast','Whole bean 12oz bag']},\\n]\\ndf = pd.DataFrame(products)\\ndf\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Template-Based Generation\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"def template_description(product):\\n    features_str = ', '.join(product['features'][:-1]) + f', and {product[\\\"features\\\"][-1]}'\\n    return (f\\\"Introducing the {product['name']} — your new go-to {product['category'].lower()} essential. \\\"\\n            f\\\"Featuring {features_str}, this product delivers exceptional value at ${product['price']:.2f}. \\\"\\n            f\\\"Perfect for anyone looking for quality and reliability.\\\")\\n\\nfor _, p in df.iterrows():\\n    print(f'\\\\n--- {p[\\\"name\\\"]} ---')\\n    print(template_description(p.to_dict()))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## LLM-Based Generation\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"def llm_description(product, model='qwen3:1.7b'):\\n    prompt = f\\\"\\\"\\\"Write a compelling 2-sentence product description for an e-commerce listing.\\nProduct: {product['name']}\\nCategory: {product['category']}\\nPrice: ${product['price']}\\nFeatures: {', '.join(product['features'])}\\nTone: Professional but engaging. /no_think\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    try:\\n        r = requests.post('http://localhost:11434/api/generate', json={'model':model,'prompt':prompt,'stream':False}, timeout=60)\\n        return r.json().get('response', 'Generation failed.')\\n    except: return 'Ollama unavailable.'\\n\\nresult = llm_description(products[0])\\nprint(result)\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Template descriptions are consistent and fast** but can feel formulaic.\\n\",\"- **LLM descriptions are more creative** and varied.\\n\",\"- **For production, generate + human review** is the ideal workflow.\\n\",\"- **A/B test descriptions** to measure impact on conversion rates.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
